        <head>Trust</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>I trust you like I trust the chains </l>
          <l> Or anyone I can </l>
          <l> Can you remember the way </l>
          <l> When every lane </l>
          <l> You burning in flames </l>
          <l> Trust in you like playing with fire in flames </l>
          <l> Can you escape from hell? </l>
          <l> Can you imagine what caused the pain? </l>
          <l> I really wanna take you away </l>
          <l> Hiding place where no one can contain </l>
          <l> The shit I'm writing today </l>
          <l> You trusted me in vain </l>
          <l> Whatever happens you'll be safe in those hands </l>
          <l> Safe without no man </l>
          <l> I trusted you in vain</l>
        </lg>
